scripts.test:nextest: cargo llvm-cov nextest --profile meta --lcov --output-path lcov.info --no-tests pass
scripts.test: pnpm run test:nextest -r --locked && pnpm run test:doctest -r --locked && pnpm run test:rustdoc -r --locked
scripts.dev-test: pnpm run test:nextest && pnpm run test:doctest && pnpm run test:rustdoc
